# Implementation Plan: Redesign index.html UI

## Goal
Redesign [index.html](file:///Users/yut/TaijiFlow/index.html) to match [data_collector.html](file:///Users/yut/TaijiFlow/data_collector.html) style for consistent design.

---

## Proposed Changes

### Layout Changes

| Component | Before | After |
|-----------|--------|-------|
| **Video** | ~50% width (panel right) | **~100% width** (full) |
| **Level Select** | 3 Buttons | **Dropdown** |
| **Control Buttons** | 1 Toggle | **1 Toggle** (keep) |
| **Right Panel** | Exists | **Remove** |
| **Instructions** | Right panel | **Bottom** (like data_collector) |

---

### Files to Modify

#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///Users/yut/TaijiFlow/index.html)

